    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Flower vases that were intended to be hung during the celebration of the tea ceremony. They are generally flat on one side and can be made of basketwork or ceramic. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
